20:52.210 --> 20:54.463
It's not for "Olivia"?

20:55.714 --> 20:58.634
Isn't that the name of your girlfriend?
Olivia?

20:58.842 --> 21:00.928
Can't you just ask her for money?

21:01.136 --> 21:04.056
- I don't have a girlfriend.
- Mom said that you did.

21:04.264 --> 21:05.766
And her name was Olivia.

21:05.974 --> 21:08.018
