21:10.854 --> 21:15.609
- Judge Judy.
- Yeah. Judge Judy.

21:17.194 --> 21:21.156
- Don't you have a Violet tattoo?
- Yes. That I do.

21:22.491 --> 21:25.494
- Do you miss her? Violet?
- Mm.

21:26.119 --> 21:28.288
I miss her all the time.

21:28.497 --> 21:30.916
That was a quite a love story,
