21:45.097 --> 21:46.556
I remember.

21:47.140 --> 21:51.311
- So, what's the O stand for?
- Well, O is a big letter for women.

21:51.520 --> 21:55.816
- Ovaries. Origami. Openness. Orifice.
- Cheerios. Hello.

21:56.775 --> 22:00.487
