26:24.918 --> 26:27.837
- Okay...
- I got, look. <i>Feminine Mystique.</i>

26:28.046 --> 26:29.631
First edition, signed.

26:29.839 --> 26:32.217
That wine stain?
Left by Betty Friedan herself.

26:32.425 --> 26:36.346
- Mm-hm.
- This is Simone de Beauvoir.

26:36.554 --> 26:39.015
Germaine Greer,
<i>Female Eunuch.</i>

26:39.224 --> 26:41.393
And I'm gonna let you have this
Eileen Myles...

26:41.601 --> 26:44.854
- ...which is absolutely life-changing.
- Mm. Yum.

26:45.063 --> 26:49.109
Yeah. My granddaughter Googled them,
