27:26.563 --> 27:29.441
- So you want to buy them or not?
- I don't know. I'm thinking.

27:29.649 --> 27:31.985
- Do you have Tabasco?
- No, I have Tapatio.

27:32.193 --> 27:36.489
- Fine. Anything is fine.
