27:36.698 --> 27:38.825
- I'm thinking.
- Hey, um...

27:40.869 --> 27:43.330
- Is this your granddaughter?
- Yeah, sure.

27:43.538 --> 27:45.123
Sage, this is Olivia.

27:47.000 --> 27:49.461
- Oh, hi.
- I've seen pictures of you.

27:49.669 --> 27:50.879
- Really?
- Yeah.

27:51.671 --> 27:54.966
Kind of a surprise meeting you here,
