28:21.076 --> 28:24.704
- Because if you do...
- Are you fucking kidding me, Olivia?

28:25.705 --> 28:27.207
- Those are worth more than $60.
- Oh.

28:27.415 --> 28:29.501
- I can do my own haggling.
- Really?

28:29.709 --> 28:31.429
- Are you sure?
- Stop trying to be so nice.

28:31.544 --> 28:34.464
Stop trying to be so mean.
Stop being such a mean asshole!

28:34.672 --> 28:37.509
Me? Mean? I'm not mean.
At least I'm not a hypocrite.

28:37.717 --> 28:39.386
- Now I'm a hypocrite.
- Yes, indeed.

28:39.594 --> 28:42.972
Did you call me earlier?
Did you call me and hang up twice?

28:43.181 --> 28:44.474
Yes.

28:44.933 --> 28:46.935
- And you know why?
- I don't know.

28:47.143 --> 28:48.395
- I don't know why.
- Because you just want power.

28:48.603 --> 28:50.688
You wanna exert your dominance
over me.

28:50.855 --> 28:52.565
You want to be the alpha Bonobo.

28:52.774 --> 28:54.692
- No.
- Okay, just take it outside.

28:54.901 --> 28:56.528
Could I get that hot sauce, please?

28:56.736 --> 28:58.905
And why don't you pay a decent wage,
you cheap asshole.

28:59.114 --> 29:01.282
- What did you call me?
- You heard what I said.

29:01.491 --> 29:02.742
You are not a feminist.

29:02.951 --> 29:04.494
It should be illegal,
what you pay these kids.

29:04.702 --> 29:06.663
- I'm not a kid.
- It probably is illegal.

29:06.871 --> 29:09.416
You know, you're not a Bonobo, Carla.
You're a gorilla.

29:09.624 --> 29:12.544
You are a silverback male gorilla.

29:12.752 --> 29:15.922
- Okay, you know what, Grandma...
- Don't you fucking call me Grandma!

29:16.131 --> 29:18.716
