- What's wrong with you?

29:18.925 --> 29:20.260
Take your head out of your ass.

29:20.468 --> 29:22.637
For God's sake,
go back and get your doctorate.

29:22.846 --> 29:24.180
Stop working in this dump.

29:24.389 --> 29:26.349
Fuck it. Okay, shit. Fuck.

29:26.558 --> 29:28.101
- That's it. Here.
- Okay.

29:28.309 --> 29:31.646
You take your stained books
and get out of my café.

29:31.855 --> 29:34.691
- I don't want them.
- Fuck you! I don't want you to have them.

29:34.899 --> 29:36.860
Take your 60 bucks,
shove it up your ass!

29:37.068 --> 29:38.695
Could I just have the hot sauce?

29:42.574 --> 29:46.703
Give me that sack.
Give me that goddamned sack!

29:47.162 --> 29:50.498
