Is that why?

29:59.799 --> 30:01.801
- That is exactly right.
- Bullshit!

30:02.010 --> 30:05.138
I saw the real you.
I saw it, you selfish asshole!

30:05.346 --> 30:08.183
- And I still stuck around!
- And your medal's in the mail.

30:08.391 --> 30:11.895
- Well, I'm returning it!
- You neophyte! You ingénue!

30:12.103 --> 30:15.356
Solipsist! Writer-in-residence!

30:15.565 --> 30:17.692
- Ha-ha-ha.
- Okay. Nice to meet you. Bye.

30:29.704 --> 30:30.914
Goddamn it!

30:32.081 --> 30:34.334
- You sure you're okay to drive?
- Oh, I'm fine.

30:34.542 --> 30:38.463
And, baby, you can call me Grandma.
That was just me flipping out.

30:38.671 --> 30:40.298
I know.

30:43.009 --> 30:44.844
Why'd she call you
"writer-in-residence"?

30:45.053 --> 30:47.814
She's calling me a sellout because
that's how I used to make a living.

30:48.014 --> 30:50.183
You go someplace,
a private college, usually...

30:50.391 --> 30:52.393
...because that's where they have
the money.

30:52.602 --> 30:54.687
You do a few readings,
teach a few seminars...

30:54.896 --> 30:56.816
...then you leave,
because you don't have tenure.

30:57.023 --> 30:58.441
But how is that selling out?

30:58.650 --> 31:01.986
Oh, because I wasn't suffering for my art.
But I had a kid.

31:02.195 --> 31:06.157
I used to take your mom along with me
when she was little.

31:06.366 --> 31:08.701
A lot of time in cars we spent,
your mother and I.

31:09.577 --> 31:12.163
Well, at least I'm learning
some new insults.

