32:28.906 --> 32:31.909
I was so damn vain I said okay,
and then we did.

32:32.118 --> 32:35.204
And, oh, she was cute.
And so damn smart.

32:35.413 --> 32:37.665
That's the real aphrodisiac.

32:37.874 --> 32:43.254
