32:58.144 --> 33:01.856
- Grandma, do you have any more ideas?
- Yeah.

33:03.024 --> 33:04.734
Afraid I do.

33:53.074 --> 33:55.410
- What?
- No. Nothing.

33:56.119 --> 33:59.580
Wait in the car.
On second thought, come with me.

34:04.377 --> 34:07.630
- Hi. Hi, Karl.
- Elle.

34:11.551 --> 34:14.762
- What a surprise to get your call.
- Well, it's been too long.

34:14.971 --> 34:16.472
Thirty years, Elle.

34:16.681 --> 34:19.350
It's been 30 years
since we saw each other.

34:20.810 --> 34:22.978
- We're 30 years older.
- That's the way it works.

34:23.187 --> 34:25.022
It don't go backwards.

34:25.231 --> 34:28.275
- Who's the young lady?
- This is my granddaughter, Sage.

34:28.484 --> 34:33.156
- Hi.
- "Sage." Nice name. Pungent.

34:33.364 --> 34:38.202
- Want some zucchini?
- Oh, that's okay. No.

34:38.411 --> 34:41.121
- Do you?
- No. No, thank you. I'm fine.

34:41.330 --> 34:44.375
How about some corn?
