34:57.346 --> 35:01.267
- Listen, who are these people?
- My grandkids.

35:01.476 --> 35:02.810
So you've got grandkids now?

35:03.019 --> 35:06.355
I do. You're not the only one
allowed to have grandkids.

35:06.564 --> 35:09.859
- Which wife is this?
- Wife number four.

35:10.067 --> 35:14.071
Kid number five.
Grandkids 9, 10 and 11.

35:14.280 --> 35:19.869
- Jesus, you're a patriarch.
- I am. I'm biblical.

35:20.828 --> 35:24.290
- How's the corn?
- Oh, it is good.

35:24.499 --> 35:26.179
Those your own teeth
you're eating it with?

35:26.334 --> 35:28.711
- Need you ask?
- You always worried about your teeth.

35:28.920 --> 35:31.589
- You took good care of them.
- Yeah. She used to tell me...

35:31.798 --> 35:34.217
- ...brush your teeth or you'll lose them.
- Did she?

35:35.176 --> 35:37.929
You know, the teeth are the only thing
we see on a person...

35:38.137 --> 35:40.389
