when they're dead.

35:40.598 --> 35:43.643
When somebody smiles at you,
they're showing you their skeleton.

35:43.851 --> 35:46.312
- That's creepy.
- Heh. It is.

35:46.521 --> 35:50.107
- So are you married now?
- Right now, no.

35:50.316 --> 35:53.486
