35:54.070 --> 35:59.200
Sage, let me talk to Karl for a minute.
Why don't you go outside, look around?

35:59.450 --> 36:00.660
Okay.

36:06.123 --> 36:08.000
You gonna make me
a marriage proposal?

36:08.209 --> 36:11.212
- Now that you know I'm available?
- Afraid not.

36:11.420 --> 36:14.757
Just wondering if a wife
was gonna pop out from somewhere.

36:14.966 --> 36:16.926
God forbid.

36:17.134 --> 36:18.344
You wanna smoke some weed?

36:23.349 --> 36:24.559
Sure. Why not?

36:27.728 --> 36:28.771
Whoa.

36:29.689 --> 36:31.691
You mean business.

36:47.248 --> 36:50.209
Didn't think I'd be having a party today.

36:50.418 --> 36:52.920
- Care for a beer?
- Yeah.

36:58.384 --> 37:01.095
So how's your partner? Daisy?

37:01.304 --> 37:02.763
Ugh, come on.

37:03.222 --> 37:05.558
- Violet.
- Violet.

37:05.766 --> 37:08.019
- How's Violet?
- She passed away.

37:09.520 --> 37:13.941
A year and a half ago. Violet's dead.

37:14.609 --> 37:18.487
- I'm sorry. I am.
- Thanks.

37:18.905 --> 37:22.575
So listen, you told me...

37:22.783 --> 37:25.494
