I should come to you.

37:25.703 --> 37:27.371
Did I?

37:28.539 --> 37:30.875
Yes, I guess I did.

37:31.542 --> 37:33.085
About a hundred years ago.

37:33.294 --> 37:36.964
Well, I need $500. Here.

37:39.008 --> 37:41.552
I can pay you back
